<br>
Everyone in the same boat moves at the same speed. <br>
<br>
That is, not including those guilds who are made up of people entirely without day jobs, would be in the same situation. Sev would either be left up due to guilds not have enough people on, in a similar situation, or killed and then those guilds would be on the rotation, and face the same wait. <br>
<br>
Those guilds who are made up entirely of people who do not work, or do not have day jobs, would make one kill, and then be on the rotation. <br>
<br>
There are a finite number of guilds on the server. Even if they could all kill sev, that's still a cap on the rotations. <br>
